quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  69,38,Ulon meusumpah ngon peue nyang taeu
  69,39,Nyang hana taeu pih saban leupah
  69,40,Keubit nyan narit rasul mulia Atra nyan geuba Neuyue le Allah
  69,41,Bukon nyan narit ureueng meupanton Gata meuiman nit that sileupah
  69,42,Jeuet keu peuingat di gata pih nit Tapi kon narit ureueng meurajah
  69,43,Tron nibak Tuhan Po bandum alam
  69,44,Meunyo buet gopnyan lagee tapeugah Geupeuna-peuna narit ateuh Lon
  69,45,Teuntee Lon hukom gopnyan le bagah Bak jaroe uneun lon mat geuh lon hue
  69,46,Lon koh bak takue sinan le reubah
  69,47,Lam kawan gata hana meusidroe Nyang peutheun geuh nyoe bek Kamoe balah
  69,48,Atra nyan cit roe haba peuingat Keu ureueng nyang that takwa keu Allah
  69,49,Kamoe meuteupue lam kawan gata Na nyang duseuta gopnyan jipeugah
  69,50,Teuma atra nyan keu awak kaphe Meuhat jeuet ase meunyesai teulah
  69,51,Atra nyan beuna cit hak tayakin
  69,52,Teuseubeh takheun tapujoe Allah Takheun teuseubeh ngon nan Po gata Nyang Maha Raya Agong ngon Meugah